name: Tea Gardner (Yu-Gi-Oh!) LoRA
description:
Do you remember Tea? This is her now! Feeling old yet?

General Info

This LoRA has been trained using the Anything v4.5 model. It does a pretty good job at generating characters that look somewhat similar to Tea Gardner from the original Yu-Gi-Oh! series. The LoRA can generate her both with a ponytail and with open hair depending on your prompt and it should also be able to generate nsfw content.

Usage

The model has been trained using Kohya so you probably want to use it in the same way as you use other Kohya models. If you are Using A1111's Webui you want to move the file into the models>Lora directory.
